    <div class="row mb-5 mt-5 text-justify col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 mb-2 mt-2">BODY WRAP is an express slimming programme and a personalized treatment which allows obtaining in a short-time and with no efforts or side effects the desired body shape by reducing the excess centimeters and improving the cellulite conditions.</div>
